::Reptilica/DevilDuer::

Reptilica opens his eyes. He was in beast mode, laying in a forest. He could 
smell smoke, and could see missile fragments and mechfluid all around him. 
The Alliance bot gets to his feet, transforming into robot mode.

He looks down at himself. His internal defences seem to have repaired most of 
the damage. Reptilica takes a few steps, yelping in surprise as he falls down 
over something. He stands up, looking back at what he tripped over. It was a 
Tasmanian Devil.

"Yo, Devil, get up," Reptilica says, shaking DevilDuer's shoulder. DevilDuer 
opens his eyes.

"Are you my mommy?" DevilDuer says in a funny voice, then falling back into 
unconsciousness. Reptilica shakes his head, picking up DevilDuer and carrying 
him off toward the CR chambers.
